div.div: Genjitsu Shugi Yuusha no Oukoku Saikenki

Suddenly summoned to a fantasy world and betrothed to the princess, Kazuya Souma is crowned the new king after providing the royal family with impressive advice. To rule the kingdom, he's taking the nontraditional (and very human) route of administrative reform. In a realm of dragons and elves, will this revolutionary's unique path prove effective?
(Source: Funimation)
The third season of Mahouka Koukou no Rettousei. After the battle against The New Breed Front, Tatsuya and Miyuki enter the new "Magic Engineering Department." (Source: Crunchyroll)

After transmigrating into her favorite novel as Ethel Wallace, she realizes how ridiculous everyone is to fawn over Riena Cassius, her sister-in-law and the original female lead who regressed in the story. Ignored by the family and unable to endure the nonsense any longer, she is determined to divorce her husband and turns toward the marquis, Rienas future enemy, for help. Will Ethel escape House Cassius? Or will regression trump transmigration? And why does the marquis seem like a gentleman?
(Source: Tapas)
Otome Game no Mob desura naindaga
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

Taichi was reincarnated as Isaac, an apprentice gardener in the world of an otome game. But, looking back, Isaac wasn't even part of the game... This is the story of the interweaving lives of the Duke's daughter, Lydia, and a boy who isn't even an NPC.
(Source: MANGA UP!)
